title: Fernando Neculqueo
text:
English  Português Español



Fernando Neculqueo is an agronomic engineer. He is a data analyst interested in Sugar & Ethanol.
He advocates for Open Data, Open Science, and Open Source Software.
Since 2021, he has been part of the research team of the Sucden Brazil.
